snippet.title: 【War of GAMA】Unleash the Beast! Prepare to experience the War of GAMA world!
snippet.description:
In a world occupied by monsters and bosses, battles amongst blood pledges and castles decide who rules! 
This decade's most exciting MMO is waiting! 
Thrilling adventure is imminent,
Are you ready for the War of Gama?
